AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Group Shipments
AD_ELEMENT.DESCRIPTION: On Picking Lists that uses the Outbound location and shipments are generated automatically, just one shipment is generated for each picking list.
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: On Picking Lists that uses the Outbound location and shipments are generated automatically, just one shipment is generated for each picking list.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Pick Using Boxes
AD_ELEMENT.DESCRIPTION: If outbound document type has the field Pick goods using boxes marked, then this field will be true.
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: If outbound document type has the field Pick goods using boxes marked, then this field will be true.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Document Date
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: Date when the Picking List is done and is expected to be completed.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Incidence Type
AD_ELEMENT.DESCRIPTION: Link to the Picking List incidences types defined on the system. This incidence types allow to define action when an incidence of this type is selected when a picking list line cannot be served.
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: Link to the Picking List incidences types defined on the system. This incidence types allow to define action when an incidence of this type is selected when a picking list line cannot be served.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Generate Shipment on PL Completion
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: On Picking Lists that uses the Outbound location is used to determine if a Goods Shipment has to be generated automatically when the Picking List is completed.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Shipment for Picking
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: When a Goods Shipment is generated automatically it is mandatory to set in this field the Document Type that should be used.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Is Grouping Picking List
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: A flag to identify Grouping Picking Lists. These pick lists groups lines from several picking lists and cannot generate shipments when they are completed.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Use Outbound Location
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: When checked it is mandatory to select an Outbound location in the Picking List. Using this location goods movements are generated to move there the products. If the flag is not checked a Goods Shipment is created to ship the items from their current location.

AD_ELEMENT.NAME: Picked Quantity
AD_ELEMENT.DESCRIPTION: This field stores the amount of items picked of a specific piking list line.
AD_ELEMENT.HELP: This field stores the amount of items picked of a specific piking list line.
